<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="127" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="127">Material examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="127">
All specimens are from Sepangar, Sepangar Island, Kota Kinabalu, Sabah, Malaysia (
<geoCoordinate degrees="06" direction="north" minutes="03" orientation="latitude" precision="1" seconds="38.66" value="6.060739">06°03'38.66&quot;N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="116" direction="east" minutes="04" orientation="longitude" precision="1" seconds="0.65" value="116.06685">116°04'0.65&quot;E</geoCoordinate>
), 20 March 2018 and collected by YW Lau. 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="127">Holotype</emphasis>
